contents.title: Oscar Karma Foundation
contents.content: The Oscar Karma Foundation is a community-driven charitable initiative focused on rescuing, feeding, rehabilitating, and rehoming stray dogs through blockchain-verified donations. The organization aims to raise 1 million meals at 50 cents per meal to feed hungry stray dogs worldwide. Currently, they've raised approximately 5,000 meals (0.5% of goal). Mission Statement: The foundation operates on principles of kindness and decentralization, aiming to do good every day with honesty, and to make a difference in the lives of those who have no voice. Partnerships: Works with Oscar Army, Shiba Army, and K9 Rescue to execute charitable programs. Community: The OSCARMY drives positive change through donations and various initiatives. Notable Achievements: Supported nearly 400 rescue dogs (Team Aspin of Iloilo), Recognized as top crypto fundraiser for Kabosu 4 Kids campaign, Named in 2025 Most Impactful Awards, Direct engagement with crypto leaders including CZ (Binance). Transparency: All donations are publicly verifiable on the blockchain and shared across social media channels. Meal counts update every 15 days or after 1,000 meals reached.

contents.title: dアニメストア Comic Festival Campaign
contents.content: Campaign Title: All Complete Sets 50% OFF! dAnimeStore Comic Festival. Key Offer: Popular comics and novels' complete sets all discounted by half. Campaign Duration: Through January 12, 2026. Eligibility & Accessibility: The campaign welcomes all participants - Both members and non-members can make purchases. Purchase history remains accessible even after canceling membership, using the same account credentials. Featured Categories: The page organizes content into themed sections - Popular comics readers are consuming, Notable 2026 anime adaptations, Trending titles from 2025, Isekai and fantasy selections, Extended 50% discount period through January 31. Additional Incentives: A separate promotional layer offers coupon codes providing up to 70% discounts with a maximum reduction of 699 yen (tax included).

contents.title: Sleepia サングラス - Night-use Eyewear for Sleep Optimization
contents.content: Sleepia Sunglasses is a night-use eyewear designed to optimize sleep quality through light management. Pricing: Sale Price ¥14,800 JPY, Regular Price ¥19,800 JPY (25% discount), Outlet Option ¥9,980 JPY (minor packaging imperfections). Light Filtering Technology: The product blocks 99.9% of blue light spectrum and targets smartphone wavelengths (450nm) at 97-98% filtration rates. It also reduces green light by approximately 44% to promote relaxation and support parasympathetic nervous system activation. Performance Benefits: According to the listing, sleep onset time decreased by 30% in company testing. Design Specifications: Frame - TR90 material (Swiss-developed flexible resin), Lenses - Orange-tinted filter polycarbonate for visibility, Weight - approximately 20g, Unisex fit with free sizing, Includes case, cleaning cloth, and instruction manual. Usage Recommendation: Wear for 2 hours before bedtime to prepare the body for sleep, even while using phones or watching screens. Developer Background: Created by a former professional athlete (155 km/h recorded speed) who operates a baseball performance academy, emphasizing recovery science integration with athletic training.

contents.title: Yahoo! Auctions - Apple Extended Keyboard II
contents.content: Item Details: Apple Extended Keyboard II ADB Keyboard Kana Layout. Current Bid: ¥2,600 (starting price was ¥1,000). Auction Status: Closed (ended October 30, 2024 at 23:15). Condition: Shows signs of wear and discoloration. Description Summary: The listing describes an Apple Extended ADB keyboard with Japanese Kana character layout. The seller notes visible aging/yellowing on the exterior. Importantly, the seller states they lack ADB equipment to verify full functionality (ADB機器がないため詳細未チェックです). Key Details: Quantity 1 unit, Bids received 6, Number of bidders 4, Includes keyboard body only, Shipping from Kanagawa Prefecture, Dispatched 1-2 days after payment, Returns not permitted, Seller rating 99.7% (5,201 feedback points).
